	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am a lvl 52 wizard i am finding it hard to solo any mob higher than I , i can do it but alot of close calls . Groups r good and safe . But the best fun i have is when i group with a Druid ( just 1 ) we get the ping pong thing going and its great and fast . Find yourself a good seasoned druid and group , u will have a blast and see your exp go...<br><br><br> Its a love thing <br>wizards and druids rule in my book . You need to try it onces . You may need to train your druid .<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
