	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;  Come to the land of High Elves.  Crush Bone is prime pickings for the wiz at lvls 13+.  Groups always use a Wiz there and you can work up to lvl 30 easily just there itself.  Be careful of the groups that you pick from.  If they are inexperienced plan you escape route early.  You will learn that leason fast in the Throne Room when your group scurries like cock roaches when you turn on the kitchen light.  I have a window right at my back at all times.  But if you find an experienced group, you can work your wiz nukes, or hand to hand once the orc of choice is concentrated on someone else.  I leveled from 12 to 14 in one setting with a great group that had a few 17 lvls.  Dont turn down an offer to accompany a group that is higher than you by 5.  Just dont go much more than 8 higher.  You still get plenty of residual exp, and you lvl alot quicker than dieing.  Well, thats all I have to say about that.<br><br>    Ravenwolde  LvL 16 High Elf Wizard  TOR server<br>&nbsp;<br>Ravenwolde ArseScorcher &lt;Elusive Nomads of Norrath&gt;</td></tr>
