	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a 16 wizzy whom my Main has twinked out. She's erudite with some fairly decent gear. I have mainly concentrated on her INT and AGI with some extra mana items tossed in there. <br>I have solo'd her all the way from level 1 (with a few exceptions of course) As an erud I gained her levels around the west. starting with Qeynos, Qeynos hills. blackburrow for a short time just to get to level 12. and then, you hit 12 BLAM! your spells actually do good damage. I took her to North karana and solo'd on everything high blue to low red. Since druids love NK its releltively easy to get a SoW and if not just have a few potions handy. I have achieved 12 to 16 in a very short time. Once you get to know the safe spots in the zone and where to kite around at you're set from level 12 to 18.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;   If you are making an erudite wizzy and are planning on twinking that wizzy a bit on the INT and AGI. try this tactic. the levels will fly by from 11-16 I garuntee. just be careful of NK, be wise and good luck! <br>16 Wizzy - Scorcea<br>Povar<br>AKA 39 Pally - Moralis<br>&nbsp;<br>*Moralis Moonshayde<br>Knight of the 62nd<br>*Amberdina Ravenssong<br>Bard of the 52nd<br>&lt;Firestormers&gt;<br>-Povar</td></tr>
